cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the area of 3D reconstruction and registration of deformable objects from a single image. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also extensively uses deep neural networks, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves geometric modeling and optimization, which could fall under cs.GR (Computer Graphics).
